nodes.text: Gut-Guro was a Weequay male smuggler in the band of the Aqualish Bandin Dobah in the period following the Battle of Yavin during the Galactic Civil War. After being informed by Zalg that a group of adventurers tracked down Dobah to retrieve the droid R4-W9, he tried with Daro Blunt and Spir Fraxis to kill them.
